<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Home' }) %>
</head>
<body class="font-body text-ink">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="font-title text-5xl md:text-7xl text-gold mb-4 tracking-wider">
          Cronache del Destino
        </h1>
        <p class="text-mist text-xl md:text-2xl font-body italic">
          Un gioco di ruolo play-by-chat
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="parchment-bg rounded-lg p-8 max-w-md mx-auto shadow-2xl">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-midnight flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-3xl">⚔️</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ink/80 mb-6">
            Benvenuto, viandante. Le Cronache del Destino attendono nuovi eroi.
            Accedi al tuo account o registrati con un codice invito.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a href="/login" 
             class="block w-full py-3 px-6 bg-midnight text-gold font-title text-lg rounded hover:bg-midnight/90 transition-colors text-center">
            Accedi
          </a>
          <a href="/register" 
             class="block w-full py-3 px-6 border-2 border-midnight text-midnight font-title text-lg rounded hover:bg-midnight/10 transition-colors text-center">
            Registrati con Invito
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-mist/60 mt-8 text-sm">
        Sistema di gioco ispirato a Fate Accelerated
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
